title: 12. Red Sea Road - Ellie Holcomb
text: by Nebraskan for life Just from listening to the sample of "Find you Here" I know this album will be special! Can't wait to hear more and can't wait to download "Find You Here" a Beautiful, True, from the heart song!! Keep it up, All Glory to God!!!Thanks you, Ellie!God bless you and your family!!! Biography Born: September 12, 1982 in Nashville, TN Genre: Christian & Gospel Years Active: '00s, '10s Daughter of producer Brown Bannister and the wife of Drew from Drew Holcomb & the Neighbors, Ellie Holcomb is a CCM singer/songwriter who played in her husband's band before launching her solo career. Born and raised in Nashville, Tennessee, Holcomb began her music career in 2005 by joining her then future husband in Drew Holcomb & the Neighbors.
